content: *The jewel in the crown of the Virgin's head, representing the radiance of the twelve virtues (Meditations 12:1)

Soon you will be leaving Mondo for a world that doesn't belong here.

Are you ready for the adventure?

You are a “girl”. You will spend the rest of your life accepting and assuming your destiny as a woman.
You are not afraid to fight and, faced with conflicting social rules, you fight to break through the barriers of gender to be with the one you love.
You are also not afraid to be alone, even if you are all alone, you can still be your own friend.
The inner completeness fills you with strength.
